name: Zend2
tagline: Zend MVC 2 with Doctrine ORM ready structure
body:
zend2
=====

Zend MVC 2 with Doctrine ORM ready structure. You can use it for your site. Need to download the Doctine library only and put into /library/doctrine folder.

I shall update this framework time to time.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
